\begin_layout Subsection
Experiment 2: Comparison with related approaches
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For the sake of comparison with previous work on contour classification
 and voicing, we evaluated our approach on the vocal part of medleyDB [].

\color red
 
\color black
MedleyDB presents a higher diversity of singers and genres, and more realistic
 data in comparison to iKala, since there are many full tracks with large
 unvoiced portions.
 
